The Herald Tapiwa Bepe In this week’s section of profiling the Zimbabwe Stock Exchange (ZSE) stockbrokers, we feature Lynton-Edwards Stockbrokers  (Private) Limited. Full Name: Christopher Masendeke Title: Stockbroker Organisation: Lynton-Edwards Stockbrokers Experience: 18 years Company Profile Lynton-Edwards Stockbrokers provides a personalized and professional service. The firm has transacted for, and assisted a number of world-class companies and currently has a diverse client base made up of both local and international investors. Service Offering Lynton-Edwards Stockbrokers offers the following services; Trade Execution  on the ZSE and VFEX. Block deals -Negotiating and executing block trades on behalf of their clients. Research – They provide tailored research on specific counters, sectors and industries. Transaction sponsor – Sponsoring broker services to listed companies and to those intending to list on the ZSE and VFEX  in compliance with Stock Exchange and statutory requirements. Target Market The clientele of Lynton-Edwards Stockbrokers include local and international, individual, corporates, and institutional investors. Set minimum investment When investors go directly to Lynton-Edwards Stockbrokers to invest on the ZSE, the set minimum investment amount is  100 shares for each counter. Contact Details Phone: +263 (24) 2796505, 2700766 Email: les@lynton-edwards.co.zw Website: www.lynton-edwards.com Information provided in this article is for educational purposes only. For more information, visit www.zse.co.zw, email info@zse.co.zw, Tel: +263 24 2886830-5